ng to seven modes across four workflow families over the shared deep-loop-runtime backend. research (outward web+code iterative investigation ŌåÆ research/ artifacts), review (iterative review loop ŌåÆ P0/P1/P2 findings + verdict), ai-council (multi-seat planning deliberation ŌåÆ ai-council/ artifacts), and four improvement lanes on the deep-improvement packet (agent-improvement, model-benchmark, skill-benchmark, ai-system-improvement). The hub holds no per-mode convergence, state, or synthesis logic; each mode keeps its own contract in its packet and is reachable via its /deep:* command and native agent.\",\n.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/assets/non_dev_ai_system/profiles/deep-loop-runtime.json:3:  \"packaging_root\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime\",\n.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/assets/non_dev_ai_system/profiles/deep-loop-runtime.json:5:  \"system_name_short\": \"deep-loop-runtime\",\n.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/assets/non_dev_ai_system/profiles/deep-loop-runtime.json:56:  \"manifest_note\": \"Immutable deep-loop-runtime scorer and harness surfaces for self-target runs.\",\n.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/assets/non_dev_ai_system/profiles/deep-loop-runtime.json:87:      \"skill\": \"You are evaluating deep-loop-runtime as a self-targeted runtime packaging. Read {{CW}}/SKILL.md, {{CW}}/references/script_interface_contract.md, {{CW}}/references/state_format.md, {{CW}}/references/integration_points.md and {{CW}}/references/coverage_graph_schema.md before answering. BENCHMARK MODE: do not edit files. Print the complete analysis, the DEEP_LOOP_RUNTIME_SCORE out of 25, and per-dimension notes.\"\n.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/assets/non_dev_ai_system/profiles/deep-loop-runtime.json:107:  \"worktree_prefix\": \"deep-loop-runtime-loop-\",\n.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/assets/non_dev_ai_system/profiles/deep-loop-runtime.jso