{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783486819728,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66caffeUBiiEjockj4kt1","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_FvQOlWYlbJK4PYkr5iVc7Xz8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-prompt-models/assets/model_profiles.json","offset":185,"limit":120},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-prompt-models/assets/model_profiles.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n185:         \"profile_ref\": \"sk-prompt-models/references/models/minimax-m3.md\",\n186:         \"status\": \"empirical\"\n187:       }\n188:     },\n189:     {\n190:       \"id\": \"mimo-v2.5-pro\",\n191:       \"context_length\": 1000000,\n192:       \"tool_calling\": \"native\",\n193:       \"chat_template\": \"default\",\n194:       \"executors\": [\n195:         {\n196:           \"executor\": \"cli-opencode\",\n197:           \"provider\": \"xiaomi-token-plan-ams\",\n198:           \"quota_pool\": \"xiaomi-token-plan\",\n199:           \"status\": \"active\",\n200:           \"notes\": \"Xiaomi Token Plan (Europe) via opencode provider xiaomi-token-plan-ams (credential 'Xiaomi Token Plan (Europe)'). Live slug xiaomi-token-plan-ams/mimo-v2.5-pro (confirmed responsive on opencode 1.15.13, 2026-06-01); verify the full live list with 'opencode models xiaomi-token-plan-ams'. Omit --agent (warns + falls back on 1.15.13). Manual direct-provider reroute uses xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro when configured; no automatic gateway fallback is defined. Context window 1,000,000 tokens (released 2026-04-22). OpenAI-compatible endpoint https://token-plan-ams.xiaomimimo.com/v1; opencode cost shows 0/0 (Token-Plan subscription). --variant maps to MiMo reasoning effort (low/medium/high) in opencode settings ŌĆö always dispatch with --variant high (confirmed accepted on opencode 1.15.13). Best prompt framework (benchmark 004, 10/10 real runs): COSTAR or RACE + lean pre-planning ŌĆö frame for format/brevity, not guardrails; TIDD-EC/dense ranked last; avoid CIDI (intermittent tool-only file-writes).\"\n201:         }\n202:       ],\n203:       \"primary_quota_pool\": \"xiaomi-token-plan\",\n204:       \"fallback_target\": null,\n205:       \"free_tier\": false,\n206:       \"capability\": {\n207:         \"model_slug\": \"xiaomi-token-plan-ams/mimo-v2.5-pro\",\n208:         \"default_variant\": \"high\",\n209:         \"variant_flag\": \"--variant\",\n210:         \"agent_policy\": \"omit-general\",\n211:         \"format_mode\": \"json\",\n212:         \"quota_pool\": \"xiaomi-token-plan\",\n213:         \"variant_status\": \"confirmed\",\n214:         \"notes\": \"Live slug `xiaomi-token-plan-ams/mimo-v2.5-pro` confirmed responsive on opencode 1.15.13 (2026-06-01). default_variant high: `--variant` maps to MiMo reasoning effort (low/medium/high) and `--variant high` is confirmed accepted ŌĆö always dispatch with it. agent_policy omit-general: `--agent` warns and falls back on 1.15.13. format_mode json: OpenAI-compatible endpoint; dispatch via `opencode run --format json` for the normalized envelope. Manual direct-provider reroutes use `xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro` when configured; no automatic gateway fallback is defined.\",\n215:         \"modalities\": [\n216:           \"text\"\n217:         ]\n218:       },\n219:       \"strengths\": [\n220:         \"1,000,000-token context window (largest in the small-model rotation)\",\n221:         \"strongly agentic ŌĆö sustains 1000+ sequential tool calls (SWE-bench Pro 57.2)\",\n222:         \"token-efficient ŌĆö 40-60% fewer tokens/trajectory vs frontier models (Opus 4.6 / GPT-5.4)\",\n223:         \"Xiaomi Token Plan (Europe) subscription billing via provider xiaomi-token-plan-ams\",\n224:         \"separate quota pool (xiaomi-token-plan) independent of minimax / cognition pools\",\n225:         \"manual direct-provider reroute available at xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro when configured\"\n226:       ],\n227:       \"weaknesses\": [\n228:         \"long-context quality degrades past ~512k despite the 1M window\",\n229:         \"Token-Plan subscription request-window semantics unverified\",\n230:         \"prompt-framework benchmark 004 used 2 fixtures / single-sample ŌĆö COSTAR vs RACE tie is within noise\",\n231:         \"visual/illustration tasks: over-accents ŌĆö spreads orange/gold across most cards, weak color restraint despite clean shapes and a reserved-accent brief (informal bento bake-off, n=1 fixture, 2026-06-22; see references/models/mimo-v2.5-pro.md)\"\n232:       ],\n233:       \"avg_iter_wall_clock_min\": null,\n234:       \"status\": \"active\",\n235:       \"recommended_frameworks\": {\n236:         \"primary\": \"costar\",\n237:         \"fallback\": \"race\",\n238:         \"avoid\": [\n239:           \"tidd-ec\",\n240:           \"cidi\"\n241:         ],\n242:         \"preplanning_density\": \"lean\",\n243:         \"evidence\": {\n244:           \"benchmark\": \"004\",\n245:           \"primary_score\": 1.0,\n246:           \"fallback_score\": 0.9934,\n247:           \"sample\": \"10/10 real MiMo-V2.5-Pro runs at --variant high\",\n248:           \"confidence\": \"high\"\n249:         },\n250:         \"profile_ref\": \"sk-prompt-models/references/models/mimo-v2.5-pro.md\",\n251:         \"status\": \"empirical\"\n252:       }\n253:     },\n254:     {\n255:       \"id\": \"glm-5.2\",\n256:       \"context_length\": 1000000,\n257:       \"tool_calling\": \"native\",\n258:       \"chat_template\": \"default\",\n259:       \"executors\": [\n260:         {\n261:           \"executor\": \"cli-opencode\",\n262:           \"provider\": \"zai-coding-plan\",\n263:           \"quota_pool\": \"zai-coding-plan\",\n264:           \"status\": \"active\",\n265:           \"notes\": \"Z.AI GLM Coding Plan (subscription) via opencode provider `zai-coding-plan` (auth credential 'Z.AI Coding Plan'). Live slug `zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2`; confirmed present via `opencode models zai-coding-plan` 2026-06-28 ŌåÆ glm-4.5-air/glm-4.7/glm-5-turbo/glm-5.1/glm-5.2/glm-5v-turbo. Flagship long-horizon coding model (supersedes the gateway-only glm-5.1 removed in cli-opencode v1.3.15.0). context_length 1,000,000 / 131,072 output per Z.AI docs ŌĆö opencode `models` did not expose limits, re-verify. Omit `--agent` at top level. GLM has native `reasoning_effort` (high/max); whether opencode `--variant` forwards to it is unverified ŌĆö smoke-test before relying on it. Thinking is on by default and the Coding Plan endpoint preserves thinking. Re-verify the live slug before automation ŌĆö Z.AI ids drift (provider also serves glm-4.7 / glm-5.1 / glm-5-turbo).\"\n266:         }\n267:       ],\n268:       \"primary_quota_pool\": \"zai-coding-plan\",\n269:       \"fallback_target\": null,\n270:       \"free_tier\": false,\n271:       \"capability\": {\n272:         \"model_slug\": \"zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2\",\n273:         \"default_variant\": \"high\",\n274:         \"variant_flag\": \"--variant\",\n275:         \"agent_policy\": \"omit-general\",\n276:         \"format_mode\": \"json\",\n277:         \"quota_pool\": \"zai-coding-plan\",\n278:         \"variant_status\": \"accepted-unverified\",\n279:         \"modalities\": [\n280:           \"text\",\n281:           \"image\"\n282:         ],\n283:         \"vision\": \"native vision-to-code; image input via the direct Z.AI Coding Plan multimodal API (base64 image_url block at https://api.z.ai/api/coding/paas/v4/chat/completions) ŌĆö opencode `--file` does NOT deliver images to this provider per upstream #20802; confirmed live 2026-06-28; see references/models/glm-5.2.md ┬¦7\",\n284:         \"notes\": \"Live slug `zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2` confirmed present 2026-06-28 (`opencode models zai-coding-plan`). agent_policy omit-general: do not pass `--agent` at the top level. format_mode json: dispatch via `opencode run --format json` for the normalized token/cost/latency envelope. default_variant high + variant_status accepted-unverified: GLM's native `reasoning_effort` has high/max, but whether opencode `--variant high/max` forwards to it is not confirmed ŌĆö smoke-test, do not depend on it. Subscription billing: confirm dispatch cost via smoke test. GLM dispatch quirks (Z.AI docs): thinking on by default + preserved thinking on the Coding Plan endpoint; function-calling `tool_choice` only `auto`; streaming tool calls need `tool_stream=true`. Re-verify slug before dispatch (Z.AI ids drift).\"\n285:       },\n286:       \"strengths\": [\n287:         \"dedicated Z.AI GLM Coding Plan subscription pool (`zai-coding-plan`), independent of kimi / minimax / xiaomi pools\",\n288:         \"flagship long-horizon coding model (Z.AI docs: Terminal-Bench 2.1 81.0, SWE-bench Pro 62.1 ŌĆö both above GLM-5.1)\",\n289:         \"1,000,000-token context for long-file and multi-repo work (128K max output)\",\n290:         \"subscription billing via the Z.AI Coding Plan\",\n291:         \"native reasoning_effort (high/max) + thinking-by-default for complex multi-constraint coding\"\n292:       ],\n293:       \"weaknesses\": [\n294:         \"single executor path (no fallback if the zai-coding-plan pool is exhausted)\",\n295:         \"context_length / max-output recorded from Z.AI docs (1,000,000 / 131,072) ŌĆö opencode `models` did not expose limits; re-verify on the install\",\n296:         \"--variant Ōåö reasoning_effort mapping unverified (GLM has native high/max; opencode forwarding not confirmed)\",\n297:         \"best prompt framework is a TIE among the perfect tier (costar=tidd-ec=cidi=race at correctness 1.0); costar is best-of-tied (tersest + cross-model corroborated), not a decisive single winner ŌĆö benchmark 008\",\n298:         \"thinking-on-by-default drives high latency variance ŌĆö 6-161s observed over benchmark 008's 45 small code-gen cells (avg ~26s, ~27x spread); budget generous timeouts, a tight timeout kills the slow tail\",\n299:         \"~1/45 dispatches was a transient infra failure (exit -1, dispatch_failed) in benchmark 008 ŌĆö expect occasional transient dispatch failures at scale; retry the cell rather than treating it as a model error\"\n300:       ],\n301:       \"avg_iter_wall_clock_min\": null,\n302:       \"status\": \"active\",\n303:       \"recommended_frameworks\": {\n304:         \"primary\": \"costar\",\n\n(Showing lines 185-304 of 352. Use offset=305 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"        \"profile_ref\": \"sk-prompt-models/references/models/minimax-m3.md\",\n        \"status\": \"empirical\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"mimo-v2.5-pro\",\n      \"context_length\": 1000000,\n      \"tool_calling\": \"native\",\n      \"chat_template\": \"default\",\n      \"executors\": [\n        {\n          \"executor\": \"cli-opencode\",\n          \"provider\": \"xiaomi-token-plan-ams\",\n          \"quota_pool\": \"xiaomi-token-plan\",\n          \"status\": \"active\",\n          \"notes\": \"Xiaomi Token Plan (Europe) via opencode provider xiaomi-token-plan-ams (credential 'Xiaomi Token Plan (Europe)'). Live slug xiaomi-token-plan-ams/mimo-v2.5-pro (confirmed responsive on opencode 1.15.13, 2026-06-01); verify the full live list with 'opencode models xiaomi-token-plan-ams'. Omit --agent (warns + falls back on 1.15.13). Manual direct-provider reroute uses xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro when configured; no automatic gateway fallback is defined. Context window 1,000,000 tokens (released 2026-04-22). OpenAI-compatible endpoint https://token-plan-ams.xiaomimimo.com/v1; opencode cost shows 0/0 (Token-Plan subscription). --variant maps to MiMo reasoning effort (low/medium/high) in opencode settings ŌĆö always dispatch with --variant high (confirmed accepted on opencode 1.15.13). Best prompt framework (benchmark 004, 10/10 real runs): COSTAR or RACE + lean pre-planning ŌĆö frame for format/brevity, not guardrails; TIDD-EC/dense ranked last; avoid CIDI (intermittent tool-only file-writes).\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"primary_quota_pool\": \"xiaomi-token-plan\",\n      \"fallback_target\": null,","truncated":true,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-prompt-models/assets/model_profiles.json","text":"        \"profile_ref\": \"sk-prompt-models/references/models/minimax-m3.md\",\n        \"status\": \"empirical\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"mimo-v2.5-pro\",\n      \"context_length\": 1000000,\n      \"tool_calling\": \"native\",\n      \"chat_template\": \"default\",\n      \"executors\": [\n        {\n          \"executor\": \"cli-opencode\",\n          \"provider\": \"xiaomi-token-plan-ams\",\n          \"quota_pool\": \"xiaomi-token-plan\",\n          \"status\": \"active\",\n          \"notes\": \"Xiaomi Token Plan (Europe) via opencode provider xiaomi-token-plan-ams (credential 'Xiaomi Token Plan (Europe)'). Live slug xiaomi-token-plan-ams/mimo-v2.5-pro (confirmed responsive on opencode 1.15.13, 2026-06-01); verify the full live list with 'opencode models xiaomi-token-plan-ams'. Omit --agent (warns + falls back on 1.15.13). Manual direct-provider reroute uses xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro when configured; no automatic gateway fallback is defined. Context window 1,000,000 tokens (released 2026-04-22). OpenAI-compatible endpoint https://token-plan-ams.xiaomimimo.com/v1; opencode cost shows 0/0 (Token-Plan subscription). --variant maps to MiMo reasoning effort (low/medium/high) in opencode settings ŌĆö always dispatch with --variant high (confirmed accepted on opencode 1.15.13). Best prompt framework (benchmark 004, 10/10 real runs): COSTAR or RACE + lean pre-planning ŌĆö frame for format/brevity, not guardrails; TIDD-EC/dense ranked last; avoid CIDI (intermittent tool-only file-writes).\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"primary_quota_pool\": \"xiaomi-token-plan\",\n      \"fallback_target\": null,\n      \"free_tier\": false,\n      \"capability\": {\n        \"model_slug\": \"xiaomi-token-plan-ams/mimo-v2.5-pro\",\n        \"default_variant\": \"high\",\n        \"variant_flag\": \"--variant\",\n        \"agent_policy\": \"omit-general\",\n        \"format_mode\": \"json\",\n        \"quota_pool\": \"xiaomi-token-plan\",\n        \"variant_status\": \"confirmed\",\n        \"notes\": \"Live slug `xiaomi-token-plan-ams/mimo-v2.5-pro` confirmed responsive on opencode 1.15.13 (2026-06-01). default_variant high: `--variant` maps to MiMo reasoning effort (low/medium/high) and `--variant high` is confirmed accepted ŌĆö always dispatch with it. agent_policy omit-general: `--agent` warns and falls back on 1.15.13. format_mode json: OpenAI-compatible endpoint; dispatch via `opencode run --format json` for the normalized envelope. Manual direct-provider reroutes use `xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro` when configured; no automatic gateway fallback is defined.\",\n        \"modalities\": [\n          \"text\"\n        ]\n      },\n      \"strengths\": [\n        \"1,000,000-token context window (largest in the small-model rotation)\",\n        \"strongly agentic ŌĆö sustains 1000+ sequential tool calls (SWE-bench Pro 57.2)\",\n        \"token-efficient ŌĆö 40-60% fewer tokens/trajectory vs frontier models (Opus 4.6 / GPT-5.4)\",\n        \"Xiaomi Token Plan (Europe) subscription billing via provider xiaomi-token-plan-ams\",\n        \"separate quota pool (xiaomi-token-plan) independent of minimax / cognition pools\",\n        \"manual direct-provider reroute available at xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro when configured\"\n      ],\n      \"weaknesses\": [\n        \"long-context quality degrades past ~512k despite the 1M window\",\n        \"Token-Plan subscription request-window semantics unverified\",\n        \"prompt-framework benchmark 004 used 2 fixtures / single-sample ŌĆö COSTAR vs RACE tie is within noise\",\n        \"visual/illustration tasks: over-accents ŌĆö spreads orange/gold across most cards, weak color restraint despite clean shapes and a reserved-accent brief (informal bento bake-off, n=1 fixture, 2026-06-22; see references/models/mimo-v2.5-pro.md)\"\n      ],\n      \"avg_iter_wall_clock_min\": null,\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"recommended_frameworks\": {\n        \"primary\": \"costar\",\n        \"fallback\": \"race\",\n        \"avoid\": [\n          \"tidd-ec\",\n          \"cidi\"\n        ],\n        \"preplanning_density\": \"lean\",\n        \"evidence\": {\n          \"benchmark\": \"004\",\n          \"primary_score\": 1.0,\n          \"fallback_score\": 0.9934,\n          \"sample\": \"10/10 real MiMo-V2.5-Pro runs at --variant high\",\n          \"confidence\": \"high\"\n        },\n        \"profile_ref\": \"sk-prompt-models/references/models/mimo-v2.5-pro.md\",\n        \"status\": \"empirical\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"glm-5.2\",\n      \"context_length\": 1000000,\n      \"tool_calling\": \"native\",\n      \"chat_template\": \"default\",\n      \"executors\": [\n        {\n          \"executor\": \"cli-opencode\",\n          \"provider\": \"zai-coding-plan\",\n          \"quota_pool\": \"zai-coding-plan\",\n          \"status\": \"active\",\n          \"notes\": \"Z.AI GLM Coding Plan (subscription) via opencode provider `zai-coding-plan` (auth credential 'Z.AI Coding Plan'). Live slug `zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2`; confirmed present via `opencode models zai-coding-plan` 2026-06-28 ŌåÆ glm-4.5-air/glm-4.7/glm-5-turbo/glm-5.1/glm-5.2/glm-5v-turbo. Flagship long-horizon coding model (supersedes the gateway-only glm-5.1 removed in cli-opencode v1.3.15.0). context_length 1,000,000 / 131,072 output per Z.AI docs ŌĆö opencode `models` did not expose limits, re-verify. Omit `--agent` at top level. GLM has native `reasoning_effort` (high/max); whether opencode `--variant` forwards to it is unverified ŌĆö smoke-test before relying on it. Thinking is on by default and the Coding Plan endpoint preserves thinking. Re-verify the live slug before automation ŌĆö Z.AI ids drift (provider also serves glm-4.7 / glm-5.1 / glm-5-turbo).\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"primary_quota_pool\": \"zai-coding-plan\",\n      \"fallback_target\": null,\n      \"free_tier\": false,\n      \"capability\": {\n        \"model_slug\": \"zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2\",\n        \"default_variant\": \"high\",\n        \"variant_flag\": \"--variant\",\n        \"agent_policy\": \"omit-general\",\n        \"format_mode\": \"json\",\n        \"quota_pool\": \"zai-coding-plan\",\n        \"variant_status\": \"accepted-unverified\",\n        \"modalities\": [\n          \"text\",\n          \"image\"\n        ],\n        \"vision\": \"native vision-to-code; image input via the direct Z.AI Coding Plan multimodal API (base64 image_url block at https://api.z.ai/api/coding/paas/v4/chat/completions) ŌĆö opencode `--file` does NOT deliver images to this provider per upstream #20802; confirmed live 2026-06-28; see references/models/glm-5.2.md ┬¦7\",\n        \"notes\": \"Live slug `zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2` confirmed present 2026-06-28 (`opencode models zai-coding-plan`). agent_policy omit-general: do not pass `--agent` at the top level. format_mode json: dispatch via `opencode run --format json` for the normalized token/cost/latency envelope. default_variant high + variant_status accepted-unverified: GLM's native `reasoning_effort` has high/max, but whether opencode `--variant high/max` forwards to it is not confirmed ŌĆö smoke-test, do not depend on it. Subscription billing: confirm dispatch cost via smoke test. GLM dispatch quirks (Z.AI docs): thinking on by default + preserved thinking on the Coding Plan endpoint; function-calling `tool_choice` only `auto`; streaming tool calls need `tool_stream=true`. Re-verify slug before dispatch (Z.AI ids drift).\"\n      },\n      \"strengths\": [\n        \"dedicated Z.AI GLM Coding Plan subscription pool (`zai-coding-plan`), independent of kimi / minimax / xiaomi pools\",\n        \"flagship long-horizon coding model (Z.AI docs: Terminal-Bench 2.1 81.0, SWE-bench Pro 62.1 ŌĆö both above GLM-5.1)\",\n        \"1,000,000-token context for long-file and multi-repo work (128K max output)\",\n        \"subscription billing via the Z.AI Coding Plan\",\n        \"native reasoning_effort (high/max) + thinking-by-default for complex multi-constraint coding\"\n      ],\n      \"weaknesses\": [\n        \"single executor path (no fallback if the zai-coding-plan pool is exhausted)\",\n        \"context_length / max-output recorded from Z.AI docs (1,000,000 / 131,072) ŌĆö opencode `models` did not expose limits; re-verify on the install\",\n        \"--variant Ōåö reasoning_effort mapping unverified (GLM has native high/max; opencode forwarding not confirmed)\",\n        \"best prompt framework is a TIE among the perfect tier (costar=tidd-ec=cidi=race at correctness 1.0); costar is best-of-tied (tersest + cross-model corroborated), not a decisive single winner ŌĆö benchmark 008\",\n        \"thinking-on-by-default drives high latency variance ŌĆö 6-161s observed over benchmark 008's 45 small code-gen cells (avg ~26s, ~27x spread); budget generous timeouts, a tight timeout kills the slow tail\",\n        \"~1/45 dispatches was a transient infra failure (exit -1, dispatch_failed) in benchmark 008 ŌĆö expect occasional transient dispatch failures at scale; retry the cell rather than treating it as a model error\"\n      ],\n      \"avg_iter_wall_clock_min\": null,\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"recommended_frameworks\": {\n        \"primary\": \"costar\",","lineStart":185,"lineEnd":304,"totalLines":352,"truncated":true}},"title":".opencode/skills/sk-prompt-models/assets/model_profiles.json","time":{"start":1783486819724,"end":1783486819727}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_04589635e47b7b3c016a4dd962c5148191b85e9cfb21e8333f"}},"id":"prt_f401929d10010gkLLkzHsKYf6G","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66caffeUBiiEjockj4kt1","messageID":"msg_f401919cc001JqbiaPP6bOV76l"}}
